videos.headline: Purdue WR takes perfect pass 89 yards to the house
videos.description: Purdue QB David Blough connects with WR Cameron Posey on 3rd & long for an impressive 89-yard TD, as they inch past Minnesota 14-10.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Purdue WR takes perfect pass 89 yards to the house) 2016/11/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boilermakers run away with 60-yard TD
videos.description: Purdue WR DeAngelo Yancey goes untouched for 60-yards after connecting with QB David Blough to put the Boilermakers ahead of Minnesota 21-20.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Boilermakers run away with 60-yard TD) 2016/11/05 ESHEET
